title: Seven Shores Urban Market and Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Take-out, Bakery, Canadian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Deli cafe with a cooler that stocks local produce for sale. Mostly vegetarian, has a selection of baked goods, some vegan some gluten free. Buys and sells products at fair prices to provide a sustainable living to producers and employees.
